question - 1
https://leetcode.com/problems/power-of-three/
code is as follows-
class Solution:
    def isPowerOfThree(self, n: int) -> bool:
        v = 1
        i = 1
        if n < 1:
            return False
        elif n == 1:
            return True
        else:
            while v <= n:
                v = 3 ** i 
                if v == n:
                    return True
                    break
                else:
                    i+=1
        return False
            
